                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380820-name-1577" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-1577" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-1577" type="surname" value="LEECH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-1577" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM LEECH</persName>
                  </hi>, jun. I live with my father, a cow-keeper at Myrtle-place, Greenwich. In the afternoon of the 2nd of August, the prisoner came to my house, and asked for Lee Races—I went in to dinner—I had a chaise at the door, and this horse-cloth was in it—when I came from dinner the horse-cloth was gone.</p>
